      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-amali-saduq:56:5",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/29/1/57/5",
      "text": [
        ": رأى الصادق (عليه السلام) رجلا قد اشتد جزعه على ولده، فقال: يا هذا، جزعت للمصيبة الصغرى، وغفلت عن المصيبة الكبرى، لو كنت لما صار إليه ولدك مستعدا لما اشتد عليه جزعك، فمصابك بتركك الاستعداد له أعظم من مصابك بولدك (4)."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bilal-muhammad": [
          "And by this isnad. Al-Sadiq (as) saw a man intensely mourning his son, so he said: O you! You have mourned over the minor calamity, but you have been heedless of the major calamity. Had you prepared yourself for what would happen to your son, your mourning would not have been as intense. Your calamity of abandoning preparedness for this is greater than your calamity over your son."
        ]
      }
    },
    "verse_translations": [
      "en.bilal-muhammad"
    ]
  },
  "index": "al-amali-saduq:56:5",
  "kind": "verse_detail"
